            </div>

            <div class="experience-detail-content">

                <p class="experience-type">
                    Daily Experience
                </p>

                <h2>
                    Shark Feeding
                </h2>

                <p>
                    Watch our aquarists feed the sharks and explain their
                    diet, behaviour and importance within marine ecosystems.
                </p>

                <ul class="experience-information">

                    <li>
                        <strong>Time:</strong> 11:30 AM
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <strong>Duration:</strong> Approximately 20 minutes
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <strong>Location:</strong> Shark Kingdom
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <strong>Suitable for:</strong> All ages
                    </li>

                </ul>

            </div>

        </article>


