                <p class="experience-type">
                    Interactive Experience
                </p>

                <h2>
                    Rockpool Discovery
                </h2>

                <p>
                    Explore a supervised rockpool environment and learn
                    about sea stars, crabs, anemones and other coastal animals.
                </p>

                <ul class="experience-information">

                    <li>
                        <strong>Time:</strong> Available throughout the day
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <strong>Duration:</strong> Approximately 15 minutes
